comments: Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and does not deliver contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Booker's (PHX) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Booker does not beat Middleton (MIL) to the spot and makes body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
DiVincenzo (MIL) makes contact with Ayton's (PHX) wrist in the lane and contact causes him to lose control of the ball.
Tucker (MIL) legally contest Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Crowder (PHX) places his hand to Holiday's (MIL) side during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Middleton (MIL) briefly grasps Booker's (PHX) arm during the screen and disengages.
Booker (PHX) places his arm to Middleton's (MIL) side at the end of his drive and releases as he retreats into his step back move.
Ayton (PHX) makes marginal contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) backside during his drive as he falling already on his own.
A 24 second violation is correctly whistled.
Milwaukee signals for a timeout while neither team is in possession of the ball and they are granted the timeout.
Ayton (PHX) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during the screen.
Paul (PHX) places a resting hand to Middleton's (MIL) front and removes it without applying force defending his jump shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Bridges' (PHX) side and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Middleton (MIL) places his arm to Booker's (PHX) side as he moves alongside of him during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Booker (PHX) slightly extends his arms against Middleton's (MIL) body off ball and disengages.
Middleton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Paul's (PHX) off arm as slight extends his arm during his jump shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) makes brief contact to Middleton's (MIL) arm during his drive and he is able to move through the contact.
Middleton (MIL) dislodges the ball from Booker (PHX) before incidental contact occurs.
Ayton (PHX) extends his arm against DiVincenzo's (MIL) body off ball and contact dislodges him from his position.
Tucker (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Booker's (PHX) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact to Middleton's (MIL) body after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Johnson (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Middleton's (MIL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Holiday (MIL) places his arm to Booker's (PHX) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Connaughton (MIL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Tucker (MIL) makes elbow to elbow contact with Booker (PHX) during his shooting motion and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
